0.content1: We would like to be able to reach out to you via email to better understand the needs of your team and to provide tailored assistance if needed.
0.content2: If you require help or want to provide feedback to GitMaya, you can also contact us at: hello@gitmaya.com.

1.title: Connect to your code repository
1.content1: Choose the code repository that your team uses. Follow the installation process so that GitMaya can connect and keep track of your development metrics.
1.content2: To get you started, GitMaya will process data from the last three months. This can take a few minutes depending on the size of your organization.
